<p><strong>附录2：</strong></p>
<div class="collapsible-block">
<div class="collapsible-block-folded"><a class="collapsible-block-link" href="javascript:;">实验记录1396/8/D&nbsp;-&nbsp;视频记录</a></div>
<div class="collapsible-block-unfolded" style="display:none">
